data.description: Welcome to your cozy cottage haven, nestled by the serene Lake Dogwood in the much-loved Seven Lakes North. Imagine unwinding in a peaceful retreat where captivating water views instantly soothe your soul. At the heart of the home is a roomy great room, inviting you to relax by its warm, wood-burning fireplace. Your kitchen and breakfast area offer delightful water vistas, creating the perfect backdrop for your morning cup of coffee. Step into your screened-in porch or the deck to soak in the lake's beauty, all while enjoying a yard that's easy to care for. You'll also find a spacious, covered front porch and a convenient circular driveway. Just a leisurely walk to Sequoia Point and a quick drive to historic Pinehurst, your home is set in a gated community famed for its friendly, small-town vibe. Seven Lakes is a treasure trove of activities, from golfing, horseback riding, swimming, boating, and tennis, to a fitness center and Clubhouse. Come and fall in love with this adorable cottage, where the charm of peaceful living meets the joys of a vibrant community life at Seven Lakes.
